channel.title: U guys Like that everything is 600+ Or 317 with 600+ models
channel.description:
My true love is still 317/474 the oldschool grapics, now 99% in server download is 600+ or 317 with 600+ models... the 1% are mostly bumped delta's, Or Unfinished 317/474 remakes with only 5% content.
So what happend to the 317/474 Pi's? like OverloadX and Rune-Legacy.

item.title: U guys Like that everything is 600+ Or 317 with 600+ models
item.dc:creator: @Ambokile Ambokile
item.description:
@Ambokile wrote:

[quote=“Nebulae, post:8, topic:459677”][quote author=runescape sucks link=topic=562585.msg4101844#msg4101844 date=1347580991]
I like revision that stay with themselves. Like 317 LOADING 317.

I wouldn’t mind like skillcapes in an earlier revision though.
[/quote]
This, for me too. Skillcapes seem to be the only real exception or necessity. Even a 194 with skillcapes would be great. Skillcapes are what you strive for, if there are no skillcapes what have you got to show, really?[/quote]
I agree. Before skill capes came out, how did people show off 99s?
